    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      854.39,
      539.22,
      909.07
    ],
    "text": "On the night of 19.04.2026, officers of the Police Narcotics Bureau Airport Unit carried out a raid at the airport arrivals terminal and apprehended a male suspect in possession of 2 kilograms and 190 grams of Kush, along with a female suspect found with 4 kilograms and 211 grams of the same substance.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
