    ],
    "text": "Female Pedestrian Killed in Road Accident \u2013 Melsiripura Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      837.71,
      541.9,
      892.39
    ],
    "text": "On the afternoon of 19.04.2026, a motor vehicle travelling towards Dambulla lost control and struck a group of pedestrians standing by the roadside in the Panliyadda area along the Dambulla\u2013Kurunegala road within the Melsiripura Police Division. The incident occurred when the driver collided with another stationary vehicle after veering off course.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      31.91,
      530.01,
      72.79
    ],
    "text": "Three female pedestrians and a young girl sustained injuries in the accident, along with the driver of the vehicle, and were admitted to the Polgolla Hospital. One of the injured female pedestrians later succumbed to her injuries.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      87.37,
      375.79,
      100.65
    ],
    "text": "The deceased was a 74-year-old resident of Kahawatta.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      115.21,
      445.18,
      128.49
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being carried out by the Melsiripura Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
